episodes.title: California Cults: The Dark Side of the Dream
episodes.description: "California Cults: The Dark Side of the Dream" explores the rise of infamous cults in California during the counterculture era of the 1960s and beyond. It delves into the charismatic leaders, their followers, and the tragic consequences of their movements, revealing how the search for meaning and belonging could spiral into manipulation, violence, and loss. #california #cults #crimedocumentary #history #horror #storytime #storytimes #storytelling #story #truestory #truecrimepodcast
